    java.io.Serializable

    public class InvalidAttributesException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException
    Reading the attributes in the litepal.xml file. Check all the attributes if they are valid value. If anyone of them is not under rules, throw InvalidAttributesException exception.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.0
